		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://markos.gaivo.net/blog/?p=198#comment-206795</guid>
		<description>change the function to use while instead of if ... works like a charm.
//Auto grows / shrinks a text area based on size of input text
function growTextArea(obj) {
    while (obj.scrollHeight &gt; obj.clientHeight) {
        obj.rows += 1;
    }

    while (obj.clientHeight &gt; obj.scrollHeight) {
        obj.rows -= 1;
    }
}

your text here</description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>change the function to use while instead of if &#8230; works like a charm.<br />
//Auto grows / shrinks a text area based on size of input text<br />
function growTextArea(obj) {<br />
    while (obj.scrollHeight &gt; obj.clientHeight) {<br />
        obj.rows += 1;<br />
    }</p>
<p>    while (obj.clientHeight &gt; obj.scrollHeight) {<br />
        obj.rows -= 1;<br />
    }<br />
}</p>
